						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Chennakēśavaśvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1677, Yuva, Āshāḍha śu. 5,</hi> corresponding to 1755 A.D., July 14, Monday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It records the renovation of the temple of Chennakēśava at Vellaṭūru and grant of land for the maintenance of worship and lamps in the temple.</p>						

						</summary>
